				<li id="16499830" class="cmnt-root" data="5" data-d="1647165090000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578924/Lusat's-Glintstone-Staff" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">13 Mar 2022 05:51</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16499830" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Just derking around, here&apos;s some extra info on FP costs. Example used will be Terra Magicus.<br/><br/>Base is 20 FP<br/>With Lusat&apos;s GS staff, 30 FP, 50%<br/>With either Lusat&apos;s or Azur&apos;s crown, 23 FP, 15%<br/>With LGS staff and crown, 35 FP 75%<br/><br/>This means FP costs don&apos;t add but multiply.<br/><br/>1.15 x 1.5 = 1.725 x 20 = 34.5 rounded up is 35 FP.<br/><br/>I don&apos;t YT much, but I figure there&apos;s a certain debate on whether impulse DPS or efficiency is truly better, let alone whether Carian Regal Scepter is the true God with Comet Azur.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16499830" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16499830" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>8</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>3</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></